snippet.title: Axel in Harlem: The Game ★ FIRST RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
★ PLAY THE GAME: https://andrewharn.itch.io/axel

I really did make it.
This game was made in 2 days in the Godot Engine as a late 2023 april fool special occasion and meme, I hope you do enjoy it!
Everything belongs to their original creators, no copyright infringements are intended.

Be sure to like and subscribe for more stuff like these!! ^^

Godot Engine, Indie, Game, Videogame, Video, Game Development, Game Dev, Meme, Shitpost, Animan Studios, I put the new forgis on the jeep, Ballin', Thug Shaker, Thug Hunter, Funny, the animan studio ballin' meme
